            "effect": "The harvest regiment engages in a coordinated melee attack against each enemy in a 5-foot emanation, with a DC 23 basic Reflex save. The damage depends on the number of actions.  \n [#] 1d8+3 bludgeoning damage  \n [##] 2d8+9 bludgeoning damage  \n [###] 2d8+12 bludgeoning damage",
